{"tid":1796032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民陣擬辦元旦遊行　警指考慮是否發不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-12-24T10:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T10:42:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3d3e30bf18314e51d098ccefc3dc23010851a2","tid":1796032,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"修訂《逃犯條例》引起的連串風波，料將持續至新一年。民間人權陣線在其Facebook專頁稱，民陣副召集人陳皓桓已就舉辦元旦遊行，向警方申請不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n民陣發貼指，擬當日下午2時由維園中央草坪出發，遊行至遮打道行人專用區。據知，該團體與警方今日(24日)將會面討論遊行安排。<br />\n<br />\n民陣副召集人陳皓桓會面後表示，警方對遊行路線等安排都無反對意見，亦未有施加須額外遵守條件，但會議上警方未有明確指出會否批出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n警方於傍晚時份回覆稱，接獲一宗擬於明年1月1日在港島區舉行公眾活動的通知。警方正與有關人士溝通，向他們了解活動細節，並會按現行機制考慮是否發出不反對通知書。"},{"pid":"1255d2ed0b90dbc17547ca4158fdb313b39b416b","tid":1796032,"uid":61615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7T7e33k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7T7e33k.jpg&h=0a5d9b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e41f1f8c7c8751abce42558259a5ce30c4018b86","tid":1796032,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1255d2ed0b90dbc17547ca4158fdb313b39b416b","tid":1796032,"uid":61615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7T7e33k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7T7e33k.jpg&h=0a5d9b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0daedbcd3b9319e22b8d6157c9392d907b987a5","tid":1796032,"uid":130001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}